page.title: 16JOBS
page.content: This is a sparsely populated area having only around one hundred and ten people in it.Most of the land is farming land so most of the people are connected with that industry.I have made a quick survey of our twelve square kilometre piece and I have found one machine worker, three schoolteachers one machine contractor, one automobile engineer,one builder, and one publican.About the three schoolteachers:one works in Longtown;one works in Carlisle; and one works in Brampton.Near Solmain there is a nursery where they grow and sell many garden plants.
